      "date": "2014-01-08 18:32:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDi, it probably makes sense to first submit and land the version of this patch that just adds \"10\" to ALWAYS_EXCEPT, let it sit for a few weeks until all of the current patches have it included, and then remove the autotest setting of INSANITY_EXCEPT=10 from the environment.  That could be done as a separate patch.\n\nThen, this patch should be rebased so that it can be properly tested.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
